    public static class WrapperCollections.ConcurrentWrapperEntrySet<K,V>
extends WrapperCollections.ConcurrentWrapperSet<Map.Entry<K,V>>
implements Set<Map.Entry<K,V>>
    Map Entry Set implementation which uses a ReadWriteLock to manage concurrent access to the underlying Entry objects.
    Since:
    Coherence 3.7
